response: *Nicholas Walter Bromley-Davenport (born 1964), High Sheriff of Cheshire 2007–08

Born in 1935, he is the son of the politician and landowner Sir Walter Bromley-Davenport. He attended Cornell University and completed his national service as an officer in the Grenadier Guards.
